{"tid":473776,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★幫兒子負擔首期及供樓，直至兒子找到工作為止","createTime":"2017-11-19T13:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T14:29:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e5ffe2b1f93330d682553b28d8a2c95270d17cf4","tid":473776,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"香港房屋協會(房協)兩個資助出售房屋項目，包括將軍澳翠嶺峰和屯門翠鳴臺，明日(20日)截止申請。不少市民今日(19日)下午趕赴位於大坑浣紗街的房協申請組交表。<br />\n<br />\n由沙田遠道而來的李太表示，今前來幫兒子交表，她指現時樓價高昂，相信兒子難獨力買私樓，而房協的兩個資助房屋項目的樓價，則或可承擔。對此兩項目，李太表示無特別喜好，直言「有就得」。<br />\n<br />\n家住將軍澳的李先生亦到場代正讀大專的兒子交表，因浣紗街位處偏僻，他一度行錯路去了勵德邨。李先生表示，如果最終成功購入單位，<span style=\"color: red;\">會幫助兒子負擔首期及供樓，直至兒子找到工作為止。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171119/bkn-20171119185735906-1119_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171119%2Fbkn-20171119185735906-1119_00822_001.html&d=EqQJC1E0smmW6Oa1XPZok1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=d89ce03e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171119/bkn-20171119185735906-1119_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f19c3e697ea3c351dda6dc62a42578a66c2fabe1","tid":473776,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"我係兒子就永遠失業了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb81df3c1af3e1333248e354e266ba18caf572c9","tid":473776,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係兒子就永遠失業了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n至少失業到供完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8932abd14492243856b8a62f9dc84d60898ae95d","tid":473776,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"以後唔返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd4187edd11f6a9c2b77a96409fd4310ccd7618","tid":473776,"uid":19